maundy thursday ( hangul : 우리들의 행복한 시간 ; rr : urideului haengbokhan shigan ; lit . our happy time ) is a 2006 south korean film directed by song hae-sung based on a bestselling novel by gong ji-young . starring kang dong-won and lee na-young , the film is about a convicted murderer awaiting execution , and the bond he forms with a suicidal young woman who starts visiting him in jail every thursday . with 3,132,320 admissions , maundy thursday was the seventh most popular korean film of 2006 .